1
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,360
The witness is here.

2
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:38,720
Linglong.

3
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,759
Official duties kept me.

4
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,520
I'm late.

5
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:42,720
Xu Kun.

6
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,800
I remember saying that

7
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,200
you Xu family members

8
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,840
are not allowed to step into the Hu family residence ever again.

9
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,759
Besides,

10
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,720
this is the ancestral hall of the Hu family.

11
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:53,720
Men,

12
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,479
kick him out.

13
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,920
Uncle Hu.

14
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,480
This is an emergency.

15
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,740
Pardon the intrusion.

16
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,720
But today,

17
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,120
I came to expose

18
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,080
Hu Wenyi's crimes.

19
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,880
Please give me

20
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,280
a moment.

21
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:12,800
Okay.

22
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:14,840
Then I will

23
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,120
give you a chance today.

24
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,160
Clan elder!

25
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,040
Shut up.

26
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,320
If you

27
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,600
don't get to the bottom of this matter,

28
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,720
then don't blame

29
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,360
our Hu family

30
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,020
for not showing you any mercy.

31
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,560
Okay.

32
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,720
Explain everything you know

33
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,120
to everyone clearly.

34
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,000
I am Wang Song,

35
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,540
boss of the Azure Dragon Stronghold.

36
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,900
I have quite a reputation on the streets.

37
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,200
Keep spouting nonsense,

38
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,480
and you'll suffer in prison.

39
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,120
Half a month ago,

40
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,600
Hu Wenyi's son,

41
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,880
Hu Dabao, came to me.

42
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:55,760
He told me to kidnap Hu Linglong at the Hu family's teahouse,

43
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:58,360
and deliver her to a Japanese man named Yamamoto Toru.

44
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,480
What nonsense are you talking about?

45
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,400
Hu Wenyi.

46
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,960
Continue.

47
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,280
I originally didn't want to mess with you Hu family members.

48
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,240
But Hu Dabao said

49
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,320
if anything goes wrong,

50
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,850
Hu Wenyi and Yamamoto Toru would cover for me.

51
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,520
That's why I agreed.

52
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,880
But at that time,

53
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,680
I accidentally started a fire in the teahouse.

54
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,680
I didn't take her,

55
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,440
so the job was ruined.

56
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,000
I didn't expect

57
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,840
they would want to kill me to silence me,

58
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,640
so I could only hide my identity

59
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,900
and lay low for a while.

60
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,840
Unfortunately,

61
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:27,040
I still fell into the hands of Inspector Xu.

62
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,040
But it's better than being silenced by Hu Wenyi

63
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,840
and Yamamoto Toru.

64
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,520
What a load of nonsense!

65
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,860
Clan elder,

66
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,600
I don't know him at all.

67
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:36,800
Luckily,

68
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,560
Yamamoto Toru is here today.

69
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,160
He can testify for me.

70
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,960
Mr. Yamamoto!

71
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,240
Mr. Yamamoto!

72
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,020
Where is Mr. Yamamoto?

73
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,640
Yamamoto Toru didn't come at all today.

74
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,280
Wenyi.

75
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,400
Clan elder.

76
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,960
Since you did it,

77
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,480
why do you dare not admit it?

78
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,520
Listen to me.

79
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,050
It's fine if Yamamoto Toru isn't here.

80
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,560
I'll look for him later.

81
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,960
Let him confront him face to face.

82
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,000
Hu Wenyi.

83
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:03,610
Don't worry.

84
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:07,040
I have already sent someone to invite Yamamoto Toru.

85
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,300
While waiting for him,

86
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,200
why don't we have a chat first about

87
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:12,280
how you poisoned and killed

88
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,560
the former head of the Hu family?

89
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:17,760
Me?

90
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,560
Hu Wenyi,

91
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,840
you are worse than a beast.

92
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,600
Elder,

93
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,600
you can't just listen to their side of the story.

94
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,240
They must be colluding

95
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,600
to take back the position of the family head.

96
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,360
Hu Wenyi,

97
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,400
you ruthlessly poisoned my father.

98
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:36,720
Do you admit

99
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,840
to this crime?

100
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,080
What a joke.

101
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,690
How could I possibly

102
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,420
poison my eldest brother?

103
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,000
Elder,

104
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,730
please be the judge.

105
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,280
If you hadn't sent someone every day

106
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,520
to give my father the so-called soothing tea,

107
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,580
how could he have this heart disease?

108
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,240
This

109
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,320
is a letter between my father

110
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,980
and a friend before his death.

111
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,560
The letter

112
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,120
clearly states that

113
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,400
you would send someone every month

114
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,240
to give my father soothing tea.

115
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,160
If you think I forged this letter,

116
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,560
we can invite that friend

117
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,160
to testify.

118
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:12,680
Wenyi,

119
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:15,160
since this is true,

120
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,940
why don't you admit it?

121
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Elder.

122
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,840
My brother Wenyi

123
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,660
often brings me soothing tea.

124
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,680
I drink a cup a day.

125
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,120
It is said to cure heart disease.

126
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,980
I felt a little uncomfortable when I first drank it.

127
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,280
After a while,

128
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,080
it might take effect.

129
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,560
Wenzhong,

130
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,520
I let you down.

131
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,440
Hu Wenyi,

132
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,320
you are simply

133
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,720
worse than a beast.

134
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,240
Oh,

135
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,480
I remember now.

136
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,400
Blame it on my busy schedule.

137
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,440
I left these trivial matters

138
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,920
to the servants.

139
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,800
Over time,

140
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,920
I forgot.

141
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:03,800
But

142
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,800
the soothing tea I sent to my brother

143
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,040
was

144
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,280
a top-grade product for strengthening the body

145
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:10,520
and consolidating the foundation.

146
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,800
It is indeed a good thing.

147
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,160
But you added aconite,

148
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:18,240
which made it a heart-burning and bone-corroding poison.

149
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,160
Aconite.

150
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,920
That's because I usually have headaches

151
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,580
and need aconite as medicine.

152
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,560
If you don't believe me,

153
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,880
you can ask Dr. Li from Jishitang.

154
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,000
A slight error in aconite dosage,

155
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,800
and it can turn into poison.

156
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,040
Your headache

157
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,560
was cured half a year ago.

158
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,640
Why were you still buying it until last month?

159
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,480
But once my father passed away last month,

160
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,680
you stopped buying aconite this month.

161
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,820
I presume I don't need to say more.

162
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,159
The reason for this

163
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,159
is self-evident.

164
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,200
As for the calming tea you sent before,

165
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,600
my father kept some of it.

166
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,020
To be absolutely sure,

167
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,120
last night Patrolman Xu and I

168
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,240
went to my father's grave

169
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,240
and exhumed his body for an autopsy.

170
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,760
Uncle Hu.

171
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,720
Everyone,

172
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,840
fellow villagers.

173
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:09,760
This morning the yamen's coroner submitted the autopsy report,

174
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,520
confirming

175
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,640
that Hu Wenzhong

176
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,920
died of poisoning.

177
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,600
The poison in his body,

178
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,560
just like the poison in this wine,

179
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,960
is aconite.

180
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,520
Hu Wenyi,

181
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:21,000
if you still want to argue,

182
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,040
why don't

183
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:24,120
we take this to court?

184
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,600
Clan Elder!

185
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,300
Clan Elder!

186
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,760
Give me a little time.

187
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:30,480
I will definitely prove my innocence.

188
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,200
Clan Elder!

189
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,120
Hu Wenyi!

190
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,240
Clan Elder, please believe me!

191
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,480
From now on,

192
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,320
our Hu family

193
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,360
will no longer have such a

194
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,320
shameless person like you.

195
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,000
Get out!

196
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,880
Clan Elder,

197
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,400
I'm wronged!

198
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,560
I am innocent, Clan Elder!

199
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,920
Look for yourself

200
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,800
at what is written on this!

201
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,840
How dare you!

202
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,600
I didn't expect you to be so shameless.

203
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,720
To do something so despicable.

204
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,000
Wenzhong,

205
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,560
I have failed you,

206
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:07,840
and I have failed Nianci!

207
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,520
Hu Linglong!

208
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,000
Get them!

209
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
Beat them out of the ancestral hall!

210
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,560
Come on!

211
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,560
I'll reward whoever does it with ten taels of silver!

212
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,080
No,

213
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,240
one hundred taels!

214
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,440
Come on,

215
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,160
come!

216
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,760
Fine.

217
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,520
You're too scared, aren't you?

218
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,160
Fine,

219
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,160
I'll do it myself!

220
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,360
I will kill you!

221
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,039
Stop!

222
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,000
Hu Wenyi,

223
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,400
just try to touch a single hair on her head!

224
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,330
Magistrate Lou!

225
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,159
Clan Elder.

226
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,200
Please.

227
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,360
Just now,

228
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,760
I was listening outside for quite a while.

229
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:55,120
Seeing Hu Wenyi attempt to commit a crime,

230
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,720
I came out to stop him.

231
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,680
Inspector Xu.

232
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,600
I have here

233
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,960
an urgent letter that arrived a quarter of an hour ago

234
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,360
from the Beiyang Fleet.

235
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,720
Your son has arrived in Weihaiwei

236
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,600
and taken up his post on the ship.

237
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,810
He said in the letter

238
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:09,280
that he was worried Hu Linglong would be harmed

239
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:12,360
and hoped we could provide her with more protection.

240
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:15,200
I heard Hu Linglong was coming here today,

241
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,360
so I came to check on her.

242
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:20,620
Who knew I would really catch a villain committing a crime.

243
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,040
Your son is fighting bravely at the front.

244
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,680
As his folks back home,

245
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,680
we absolutely cannot let him worry.

246
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,320
Hu Wenyi.

247
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,600
The evidence of your poisoning Hu Wenzhong

248
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,560
is irrefutable.

249
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:33,000
For a wicked person like you,

250
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,760
I will definitely punish you severely.

251
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:35,490
Take him away

252
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,760
and put him in jail.

253
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,320
Elders.

254
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:41,760
Please.

255
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,560
Take him away.

256
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,000
Go.

257
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,160
Go.

258
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,360
Elders.

259
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,160
Father,

260
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:02,120
I'm late.

261
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,760
What happened?

262
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:06,360
Take Hu Dabao away as well.

263
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:22,480
Thank you, Uncle Xu, for your great help this time.

264
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,480
It's just my duty.

265
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,980
No need to thank me.

266
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:26,880
Besides,

267
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,970
this was also Zhinian's

268
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,800
request before he left.

269
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,800
To secretly investigate

270
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,280
and find these evidence,

271
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,160
he must have

272
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,240
taken a lot of pains.

273
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,130
If you really want to thank him,

274
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,530
wait until he comes back

275
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,240
and thank him yourself.

276
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,160
Zhinian.

277
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,600
Did he reply?

278
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,160
No reply yet.

279
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,840
But it should be soon.

280
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,320
Linglong,

281
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,600
previously,

282
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,680
I stopped Zhinian

283
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,120
from seeing you.

284
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,200
Don't blame him.

285
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,410
I did have prejudices against you before,

286
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,080
but after this incident,

287
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,720
I can understand

288
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,680
why he

289
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,520
is so devoted to you.

290
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:29,760
Uncle.

291
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,800
Then I will take my leave.

292
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,360
Hu Linglong.

293
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:55,800
She wouldn't really leave me here

294
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,200
and ignore me, would she?

295
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,960
Then how am I supposed to go back?

296
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,040
[Sigh]

297
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:02,680
Since that day

298
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,880
she sealed me in the wooden box,

299
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:07,530
I actually can't contact her anymore.

300
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,560
I don't even have a chance to apologize.

301
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:11,360
[Sigh]

302
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:16,640
Qiao Xin.

303
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,440
Qiao Xin!

304
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:21,920
Hu Linglong.

305
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:38,000
[Hmph]

306
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:40,840
Hu Linglong.

307
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:41,880
I thought you had completely

308
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:43,120
forgotten about me.

309
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,160
I'm sorry.

310
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,400
It was wrong of me

311
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,840
to take my anger out on you.

312
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,680
I shouldn't have blamed you.

313
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,520
I've thought it through these past few days.

314
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:56,320
The ones truly at fault are Hu Wenyi and the others.

315
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,680
Before,

316
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,560
I was also too reckless.

317
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:02,880
I swear,

318
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,400
from now on, without your permission,

319
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:06,130
I will never act on my own again.

320
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,480
If I break this promise,

321
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:09,120
I will never be able to return to heaven

322
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,450
or be an immortal again.

323
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,970
You finally smiled.

324
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,440
Qiao Xin.

325
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,580
Since you are an immortal,

326
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,440
can I ask you a question?

327
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,800
What question?

328
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,200
Tell me.

329
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:28,360
Will I ever see my parents again?

330
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,080
Definitely.

331
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,360
Did you know?

332
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:35,960
There is a river in the sky

333
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,160
called the Milky Way.

334
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,160
Simply put,

335
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,480
it's like the passengers on a riverbank.

336
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:43,980
They have now reached the other side,

337
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:44,760
while you

338
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,260
are still at the crossing.

339
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:49,200
As long as you always remember them,

340
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:51,280
many, many years later,

341
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,600
when you also go to heaven,

342
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:55,060
you'll find that you've become a small boat,

343
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,120
finally sailing slowly toward the other side.

344
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:57,850
At that time,

345
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,560
they will be waiting on the shore to welcome you.

346
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:00,120
Really?

347
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:01,320
Really.

348
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,160
We immortals never lie.

349
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:05,920
Mhm.

350
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:07,120
I believe you.

351
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:08,760
Tonight,

352
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,400
I'm going to find them in the sky.
